    <h4 class="news-story-title">
        
            <a target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" href="https://www.rattle.com/this-is-how-i-make-my-money-by-heather-bell/">“This Is How I Make My Money” by Heather Bell</a>
        
    </h4>

<div class="row">
    
        <div class="news-story-body col-xs-12">
            <div class="news-story-byline">
                
                    
                        <a rel="nofollow" class="timeago" title="Mar 07, 2022" href="/link/oOf2XC/this-is-how-i-make-my-money-by-heather-bell">a day ago</a>
                    
                    
                
                
                    
                    
                
                
                    
                        &nbsp;|&nbsp;
                    
                
                



    
    
        <a href="/media-outlet/rattle" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Rattle</a>
        
    
    


            </div>
            
            
                
                    Heather BellTHIS IS HOW I MAKE MY MONEYEvery time a possible employer called me&nbsp;in response to a resume I had submitted, they&nbsp;would awkwardly ask, “and when are you available&nbsp;for an interview?” And I had to&nbsp;casually say back, “oh, anytime,” as if it wasNo Big Deal. You see, No Big Deal behavior is&nbsp;actually similar to a duck walking splay-leggedto the edge of a pond. Oh, I’ll get there,and I will desperately pretend I can walk normally&nbsp;the whole way. At this point I had been unemployed&nbsp;for 4 months.
                
                
            
        </div>
    
    
