    <h4 class="news-story-title">
        
            <a target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" href="https://www.rattle.com/after-my-teenager-tries-to-kill-herself-i-dream-everyone-is-turning-into-zombies-by-elizabeth-johnston-ambrose/">“After My Teenager Tries to Kill Herself, I Dream Everyone Is Turning into Zombies …” by Elizabeth Johnston Ambrose</a>
        
    </h4>

<div class="row">
    
        <div class="news-story-body col-xs-12">
            <div class="news-story-byline">
                
                    
                        <a rel="nofollow" class="timeago" title="Mar 04, 2022" href="/link/oOKIG2/after-my-teenager-tries-to-kill-herself-i-dream-everyone-is-turning-into-zombies-by-elizabeth-johnston-ambrose">4 days ago</a>
                    
                    
                
                
                    
                    
                
                
                    
